      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it seriously looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a total dream and has been kept spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been perfectly cared for and is ready to hit the road today, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
