    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s M-division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, the drivetrain delivers linear power to a factory limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventive maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic turn-in and balanced damping these units are celebrated for. Presented in showroom condition with flawless paint depth and a pristine Nappa leather cockpit, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
