    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior is flawless, with the original factory paint holding a deep, glass-like finish free of any stone chips or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the leather is supple without any bolster wear, and the controls retain their factory-fresh tactile feel. Mechanically, this car is perfect, supported by a complete, documented service history from the same authorized dealership since day one. It includes all original keys, manuals, and an untouched tool kit. This is a rare chance to acquire a turn-key example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44800.0,
