      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to drive this beauty home. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and honestly, you won\u2019t find another one this clean out there. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
