      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerhouse utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a seamless power delivery. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains in factory-new form, with recent structural inspections confirming the integrity of the rear subframe mounting points. This specimen boasts original paint depth and a pristine interior, with comprehensive service records detailing a recent rod bearing replacement and VANOS overhaul. For the purist seeking a mechanically flawless, unmodified icon, this E46 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance.",
